    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it\u2019s completely spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new, you\u2019ve found it. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
