    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 BMW M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform. The naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 retains factory-spec compression across all eight cylinders, breathing through individual throttle bodies for instantaneous transient response. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, the drivetrain is mechanically flawless. The chassis remains taut with original bushings and a pristine carbon-fiber reinforced plastic roof, maintaining a low center of gravity. Dressed in original Alpine White paint with zero swirl marks, this collector-grade specimen features an interior devoid of bolster wear or dash UV degradation. Full service documentation confirms proactive rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring long-term mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2020 Sedan. Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Title in hand.",
