    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle presents in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously preserved by a single owner in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single stone chip or parking lot blemish. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the hand-stitched leather is soft and uncreased, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Every electronic component, from the premium surround-sound system to the adaptive cruise control, functions as it did the day it left the factory. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed strictly by brand specialists. This is not just a used car; it is a pristine example of automotive excellence, offering a 'new car' experience at a pre-owned value. Full service records, both keys, and a clean title are ready for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
