    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute gem! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in pristine condition\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out with any questions; I'm super happy to chat and tell you more about it!",
