    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available now is an exceptional FD3S chassis, powered by the iconic 13B-REW twin-rotor engine. This specimen retains its original sequential twin-turbocharged induction system, meticulously maintained to ensure seamless transition between the primary and secondary turbines. The front-midship engine placement provides a perfect 50/50 weight distribution, paired with a lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension for surgical handling. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the apex seals demonstrate excellent compression, and the five-speed manual transmission delivers tactile, precise shifts through a factory-spec Torsen limited-slip differential. Free of heat-cycling fatigue in the vacuum system and preserved in its original aerodynamic profile, this is a definitive collector-grade example of Japanese engineering excellence.",
